description: Mentioned only by Audsley in a footnote in which he quotes Seidel as follows: �Man findet dies Register [Gemshorn] im Manual zu 8', 4', 2' und 1', zu letzten beiden Grössen zuwrilen unter dem Namen Super-Gemshorn.� In English: �One finds this stop [Gemshorn] at 8', 4', 2' and 1', the last two sizes occasionally under the name Super-Gemshorn.�
